				<span class="help-qa-letter">Q18.</span>  Are you planning improvements and new GeoGem features in the future?  
			</p>
			<p class="help-answer-para">
				<span class="help-qa-letter">A:</span> Absolutely! We are working to 1) improve the current GeoGem experience, and
				2) looking for new ideas to incorporate into GeoGem.
			</p>
			<hr class="help-line">
            <p>
				<span class="help-qa-letter">Q19.</span> What does the name GeoGem mean? I don’t get it.
			</p>
			<p class="help-answer-para">
				<span class="help-qa-letter">A:</span> We chose GeoGem as our product name because it’s easy to spell and remember, 
				it’s alliterative, and mostly, because it’s fun! It’s technical meaning is less important… some stuff to do with the
				geo-shapes in our system and background wallpaper, and there are gems in the Rails framework we used to program the 
				system.
			</p>
            <hr class="help-line">
            <p>
				<span class="help-qa-letter">Q20.</span> That wasn’t helpful enough. Is there anyone I can contact for more help?
			</p>
		
			<p class="help-answer-para">
